        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="pandas修改列的顺序（移动列）"><a href="#pandas修改列的顺序（移动列）" class="headerlink" title="pandas修改列的顺序（移动列）"></a>pandas修改列的顺序（移动列）</h1><p>方法一：按照列名排序</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import pandas as pd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">data = pd.DataFrame([[1,2,3],</span><br><span class="line">                     [2,5,6],</span><br><span class="line">                     [3,8,9]], columns=[&#x27;b&#x27;, &#x27;c&#x27;,&#x27;a&#x27;])</span><br><span class="line">order = [&#x27;a&#x27;, &#x27;b&#x27;, &#x27;c&#x27;]</span><br><span class="line">data = data[order]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>方法二：先把需要调整的列拿出来，再插入指定位置</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># d= data.drop(&#x27;a&#x27;,axis=1)</span></span><br><span class="line">d = data.pop(<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">data.insert(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>, d)   <span class="comment"># 在第1列的位置，添加列名为a的列d (d是数据)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
